rows.label: qst650402_msg0003
rows.name: Yeah... I think it must be Raymon.

rows.label: qst650402_msg0005
rows.name:
Oh, aye, thanks... I
think I'll pull through.

rows.label: qst650402_msg0006
rows.name:
Raymon, do you know where Nascion
and the others have got to?

rows.label: qst650402_msg0007
rows.name:
God, you're right... We
have to save the kids...!

rows.label: qst650402_msg0008
rows.name: You sit back and let us take charge.

rows.label: qst650402_msg0009
rows.name:
Yeah, we'll get 'em back
for ya. Zeke's honor.

rows.label: qst650402_msg0011
rows.name:
Nascion, Arin, and Arina got
taken captive by some Ignas...

rows.label: qst650402_msg0013
rows.name:
First time I've heard of any
Ignas round these parts...

rows.label: qst650402_msg0014
rows.name:
Aye, they're not native to
here. Must've come from some
other Divine Beast...

rows.label: qst650402_msg0015
rows.name:
It would seem best to drive
them out before it's too late.

rows.label: qst650402_msg0016
rows.name:
D'you know where those
Igna lowlifes took them?

rows.label: qst650402_msg0018
rows.name:
They were headed towards
the Isle of Urchon.

rows.label: qst650402_msg0019
rows.name:
Got it! Let's go! Come on, guys,
hup to it! We gotta move! Now!
